  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether coronary artery CT scanning or nuclear
      stress testing is better at diagnosing chest pain patients with known coronary artery disease
      to select appropriate candidates for coronary catheterization and re-vascularization.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
